{"tid":1738032,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港急需一個大遊行","createTime":"2019-11-19T06:21:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T07:40:47.000Z","uid":102076,"like":26,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8f151d2ff7ba1ba4e520ef114223ff7d2cbf73b3","tid":1738032,"uid":102076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:21:56.000Z","msg":"黎明行動係好成功，但從外界角度出發<br />\n好易會標籤咗我地為少數「破壞」公物嘅黑衣人<br />\n加上兩間大學嘅戰場<br />\n好多陣地戰嘅目標都係救人為主<br />\n呢個時候明白大家一定好攰、心情亦好差<br />\n但無可否真係好需要一個大遊行<br />\n去正視聽由始至終，我地都係五大訴求<br />\n同時亦係向政府談判：再無回應，我地只會繼續行動，繼續罷工罷課<br />\n矛頭重新指向政府<br />\n所以呢個星期急需全港大型遊行<br />\n但絕非打陣地戰，只係由民陣上水，去集合返民意"},{"pid":"727f869a0ec88ba9af88fb81b6bf25966ad1c9a1","tid":1738032,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:23:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c006da6a1939aa45d080d3b5d51c2ca54e193c06","tid":1738032,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:23:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4adec29ee35d91c225cc68a2861e9d0c719f78","tid":1738032,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:23:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9131b4c568fc15c766e77c5b26beb418e9c8646","tid":1738032,"uid":102076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:23:56.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"26981c459aa1cb7303c5b27a508ba902ad4378e0","tid":1738032,"uid":102076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:24:06.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"ca52abdea5f20b1ea964c770ecd9a8c745c561e4","tid":1738032,"uid":102076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:24:19.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"e0d5b4ea4aa4410607f6fb0cf02dca622f22fe6f","tid":1738032,"uid":76310,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:24:30.000Z","msg":"